Package org.zoolu.sip.message

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseMessage
    Class BaseMessage implements a generic SIP Message.
    BaseMessageFactory
    BaseMessageFactory is used to create SIP messages, requests and responses by means of two static methods: createRequest(), createResponse().
    BaseMessageOtp
    Class BaseMessageOtp implements a generic SIP Message.
    BaseSipMethods
    Class BaseSipMethods collects all SIP method names.
    BaseSipResponses
    Class SipResponses provides all raeson-phrases corrspondent to the various SIP response codes
    Message
    Class Message extends class sip.message.BaseMessage adding some SIP extensions.
    MessageFactory
    Class sipx.message.MessageFactory extends class sip.message.BaseMessageFactory.
    SipMethods
    Class SipMethods extends org.zoolu.sip.message.BaseSipMethods and collects all SIP method names.
    SipResponses
    Class SipResponses provides all raeson-phrases corrspondent to the various SIP response codes
